Interface DataStore.DetailedData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlocksData.DetailedDestroyerdBlocksEntry, BlocksData.DetailedPlacedBlocksEntry, DeathsData.DetailedDeathEntry, ItemsData.DetailedDroppedItemsEntry, ItemsData.DetailedPickedupItemsEntry, ItemsData.DetailedUsedItemsEntry, PlayersData.DetailedLogPlayersEntry, PVEData.DetailedPVEEntry, PVPData.DetailedPVPEntry
    Enclosing interface:
    DataStore

    public static interface DataStore.DetailedData
    Represents data stored in a log format, i.e. new data is appended to the end of the table. No existing data can be changed.
    Multiple instances of this type could (and should) exist.
